The '''House of Adasca''' was a very rich [[Noble/Legends|noble]] family on [[Arkania/Legends|Arkania]], formed of [[Arkanian/Legends|Arkanian]] purebloods. They owned [[The Adasca BioMechanical Corporation of Arkania|Adascorp]]. They were friends with the [[Draay family]] for a few generations.

